" Tabularize

nmap <silent> `= :Tabularize /^[^=]\+\zs=[&>]\?<CR>
" xmap <silent> `= :Tabularize /^[^=]\+\zs=[&>]\?<CR>
nmap <silent> `; :Tabularize /^[^:]\+\zs:<CR>
" xmap <silent> `; :Tabularize /^[^:]\+\zs:<CR>
nmap <silent> <Leader>t= :Tabularize /^[^=]\+\zs=[&>]\?<CR>
xmap <silent> <Leader>t= :Tabularize /^[^=]\+\zs=[&>]\?<CR>
nmap <silent> <Leader>t: :Tabularize /^[^:]\+\zs:<CR>
xmap <silent> <Leader>t: :Tabularize /^[^:]\+\zs:<CR>

